# Search Knowledge Base

Search your project's documentation using hybrid semantic + keyword search.

## Usage

```
/lsearch <query>
```

## Arguments

- `query` (required): Search query

## Examples

```
/lsearch authentication flow
/lsearch deployment process
/lsearch API documentation
```

## Your task

Use lsearch to search the knowledge base with the provided query and return relevant results.
